title: Darryl's Books Worldwide
name: Darryl's Books Worldwide
description:
A Map by Darrylsloan

I'm a self-published science fiction novelist, distributing my books directly into readers' hands via sales from my website (www.darrylsloan.com). This map shows my where my readers live around the world, accurate to the nearest town.
